description:
Team Skull Grunts are nasty bunch of people that will force people into battling them if you don`t watch your words and then try to take their opponents Pokémon as their prize for winning the battle. Zipp has multiple Yungoos`s but it is virtually impossible to determine the difference.
Zipp`s Yungoos all attacked at the Pokémon School but they were no match for Kiawe`s Turtonator`s Dynamic Full Flame and all 3 of them were defeated.
name: Youngoose (Zip)
